    "facility": "GKN Aerospace, Garden Grove, CA",
    "started_iso": "2026-05-21T22:40:00Z",
    "status_headline": "Incident fully resolved. All evacuation orders lifted May 27 at 7:30 PM PDT. All roads \u2014 including Western Ave \u2014 fully reopened May 28. Only a 300-ft exclusion zone remains around the GKN tank as hazmat crews treat solidified MMA. GGUSD 12 campuses reopened today for the final day of the school year. DA criminal investigation and class-action lawsuits ongoing.",
